#==================================================================
# General Visual Studio / .NET generated files
# Recommended: https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/VisualStudio.gitignore
#==================================================================

## Ignore Visual Studio temporary files, build results, and user-specific files
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## Ignore NuGet packages folder (older style)
# Usually, packages are managed globally now, but good to include for older projects.
packages/
*.nupkg

## Ignore Roslyn classification cache
*.rsuo

## Ignore files produced by Visual Studio testing
*.cache
*.trx
TestResults/
*.coverage
*.coveragexml

## Ignore build output folders
**/[Bb]in/
**/[Oo]bj/

## Ignore Visual Studio Generated code folders
Generated\ Files/

## Ignore Visual Studio Code specific settings
.vscode/

## Ignore Rider specific settings
.idea/

## Ignore publish output
**/[Pp]ublish/


## Ignore Windows image file caches
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
ehthumbs_vista.db

## Ignore Windows Content Indexer/Search Folder metadata files
[Dd]esktop.ini

## Ignore Mac OS metadata files
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride


## Ignore log files
*.log

## Ignore local temp files
*.tmp

## Ignore local backup files
*.bak
